    "In additive attention, the weight matrix of the key is generated for the key, while in conv-attention, the weight matrix of the key is related to the query.",
    "Based on the excellent performance of softmax in self-attention, the softmax function is still retained.",
    "Model StructureIn practice, to represent a linear structure (like the structure of W T j k + b j) in a network is usually achieved using a fully connected layer, which is done by expanding the feature map into a one-dimensional vector and multiplying it by a weight vector.",
    "Instead of a fully connected layer, the principle of using a 1 * 1 convolution module proposed by NIN [19] is the same as that of a fully connected layer.",
    "When 1 * 1 convolution is used, then the weight vector is the convolution kernel, and the input data is multiplied element by element with the convolution kernel, and the bias is added after summation, which is consistent with the formulation of 6.We view this operation as a kind of \"implicit classification\"."
